        Set ORF attributes.
        Parameters:
        id - ID of the region in the database
        begin - Start position on the transcript
        end - Stop position on the transcript
        size - Length of the ORF
        strand - Either forward or reverse
        coding - coding or noncoding
        type - inner or outter or none
        seq - region sequence
        transcript_id - ID of the transcript in the database
